 Galvatron turned to Like Like. "Yes on my signal we will run towards the 
sheilds. Guiledart go bring two of the bombs to darkefate."  Guiledart nodded 
and flew infront of darkefate avoiding fire as he went. "ON his signal run at 
the sheilds. When you get 10 feet from them throw the bombs. They will  
explode 5 feet from the sheilds. It will create a temporary hole in the 
sheilds for 15 seconds. Get you men through. I have been instructed to give 
you these two bombs. Use them well."

--part1_76.8146cac.27cac367_boundary
